title: Ebro In The Morning - Greatest Hip-Hop Collabs of All-Time + The White Privlege Card
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 8/5/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio talking about the greatest hip-hop collabs of all-time, Brittney Griner's sentence in Russian prison, and the white privilege card. 

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning! 

Subscribe to "Summer Jam: Through The Years" - hosted by Laura Stylez!
